#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.81"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.81:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.81:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga "
msgstr "9. Mindfulness "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.81:0.3"
msgid "81. Satisampajaññasutta "
msgstr "81. Mindfulness and Situational Awareness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.81:1.1"
msgid "“Satisampajaññe, bhikkhave, asati satisampajaññavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti hirottappaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when there is no mindfulness and situational awareness, one who lacks mindfulness and situational awareness has destroyed a vital condition for conscience and prudence. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.2"
msgid "Hirottappe asati hirottappavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti indriyasaṃvaro. "
msgstr "When there is no conscience and prudence, one who lacks conscience and prudence has destroyed a vital condition for sense restraint. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.3"
msgid "Indriyasaṃvare asati indriyasaṃvaravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti sīlaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is no sense restraint, one who lacks sense restraint has destroyed a vital condition for ethical conduct. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.4"
msgid "Sīle asati sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "When there is no ethical conduct, one who lacks ethics has destroyed a vital condition for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.5"
msgid "Sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.6"
msgid "Yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti nibbidāvirāgo. "
msgstr "When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.7"
msgid "Nibbidāvirāge asati nibbidāvirāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is no disillusionment and dispassion, one who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.81:1.8"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.81:1.9"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, satisampajaññe asati satisampajaññavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti hirottappaṃ; "
msgstr "In the same way, when there is no mindfulness and situational awareness, one who lacks mindfulness and situational awareness has destroyed a vital condition for conscience and prudence. "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.10"
msgid "hirottappe asati hirottappavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti … pe … "
msgstr "When there is no conscience and prudence … "

msgctxt "an8.81:1.11"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.337, sc2
msgctxt "an8.81:2.1"
msgid "Satisampajaññe, bhikkhave, sati satisampajaññasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti hirottappaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is mindfulness and situational awareness, one who has fulfilled mindfulness and situational awareness has fulfilled a vital condition for conscience and prudence. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.2"
msgid "Hirottappe sati hirottappasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti indriyasaṃvaro. "
msgstr "When there is conscience and prudence, a person who has fulfilled conscience and prudence has fulfilled a vital condition for sense restraint. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.3"
msgid "Indriyasaṃvare sati indriyasaṃvarasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti sīlaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is sense restraint, one who has sense restraint has fulfilled a vital condition for ethical conduct. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.4"
msgid "Sīle sati sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "When there is ethical conduct, one who has fulfilled ethical conduct has fulfilled a vital condition for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.5"
msgid "Sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.6"
msgid "Yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti nibbidāvirāgo. "
msgstr "When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.7"
msgid "Nibbidāvirāge sati nibbidāvirāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is disillusionment and dispassion, one who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.81:2.8"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would grow to fullness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.81:2.9"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, satisampajaññe sati satisampajaññasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti hirottappaṃ; "
msgstr "In the same way, when there is mindfulness and situational awareness, one who has fulfilled mindfulness and situational awareness has fulfilled a vital condition for conscience and prudence. "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.10"
msgid "hirottappe sati hirottappasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti … pe … "
msgstr "When there is conscience and prudence … "

msgctxt "an8.81:2.11"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti. "
msgstr "One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.81:2.12"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

